<L>__{exterior indiana police station morning}
<A>__{maurice and officer grey are seated on the front stairs of the precinct drinking coffee when adelle matlin drives up. adelle steps out of a rented toyota celica. her tense frightened eyes betray her mental state for the past ten hours. she walks to the stairs.}
